== 對恆星形成的影響 ==
2022年1月，在《自然》雜誌上的一篇論文發現，觀測和建模已經確定氣泡膨脹的表面作用，已經收集了氣體和碎片，並負責所有年輕恆星的形成<ref>{{cite web | url = https://sites.google.com/cfa.harvard.edu/local-bubble-star-formation | title = Star Formation near the Sun is driven by expansion of the Local Bubble | website = The Local Bubble | url-status = live | access-date = 7 February 2022 | archive-date = 2022-05-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220504123327/https://sites.google.com/cfa.harvard.edu/local-bubble-star-formation }}</ref>。

